category: Devel Java
requires: jamvm
sdesc: "ANother Tool for Language Recognition (runtime)"
ldesc: "ANother Tool for Language Recognition, (formerly PCCTS) is a 
language tool that provides a framework for constructing recognizers, 
compilers, and translators from grammatical descriptions containing 
Java, C#, C++, or Python actions. ANTLR provides excellent support for 
tree construction, tree walking, and translation."
